{
  "name": "WF5 \u2014 Patient Reactivation (30-Day)",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Workflow 5: Patient Reactivation\n\n**Trigger:** Every Monday at 9:00 AM\n\n**Logic:** Reads from Supabase. Finds patients inactive for 30+ days (last message > 30 days ago or never messaged), who haven't received a reactivation message yet and are not inactive/completed. Sends via Meta Cloud API (template: patient_reactivation). Sets `reactivation_sent = TRUE` after sending.\n\n**Data source:** Supabase `public.patients`\n\n**Note:** Meta category for this message is MARKETING \u2014 ensure opt-in compliance and template approval before activating.\n\n**Before activating:**\n1. Set credential on all Postgres nodes \u2192 Supabase DB\n2. Set credential on HTTP node \u2192 WhatsApp Business API (HTTP Header Auth)\n3. Ensure the `patient_reactivation` template is approved as MARKETING in Meta Business Manager",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 420
      },
      "id": "55555555-5555-5555-5555-000000000001",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        240,
        60
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "0 9 * * 1"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "55555555-5555-5555-5555-000000000002",
      "name": "Weekly Monday 9AM Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [
        240,
        380
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "executeQuery",
        "query": "SELECT * FROM public.patients WHERE status NOT IN ('inactive','completed') AND reactivation_sent = FALSE AND (last_message_sent IS NULL OR last_message_sent < NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days')",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "55555555-5555-5555-5555-000000000003",
      "name": "Read Patients from Supabase",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.postgres",
      "typeVersion": 2.4,
      "position": [
        460,
        380
      ],
      "credentials": {
        "postgres": {
          "id": "REPLACE_WITH_SUPABASE_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "Supabase DB"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Filter patients inactive for 30+ days who haven't been reactivated\nconst items = $input.all();\nconst tz = $env.TIMEZONE || 'Asia/Kolkata';\nconst inactivityDays = 30;\n\nconst now = new Date();\nconst thresholdDate = new Date(now);\nthresholdDate.setDate(thresholdDate.getDate() - inactivityDays);\n\nconst filtered = items.filter(item => {\n  const p = item.json;\n\n  if (p.status === 'inactive' || p.status === 'completed') return false;\n\n  // reactivation_sent is boolean in Supabase\n  if (p.reactivation_sent === true) return false;\n\n  if (!p.phone || !/^\\+[1-9]\\d{6,14}$/.test(p.phone)) return false;\n\n  if (p.last_message_sent) {\n    const lastSent = new Date(p.last_message_sent);\n    if (lastSent > thresholdDate) return false;\n  }\n\n  return true;\n});\n\nif (filtered.length === 0) {\n  return [{ json: { _skip: true, reason: 'No inactive patients to reactivate this week' } }];\n}\n\nreturn filtered.map(item => ({\n  json: {\n    ...item.json,\n    _workflow: 'workflow-5-reactivation',\n    _message_type: 'reactivation',\n    _to_phone: item.json.phone.replace(/^\\+/, ''),\n    _name: item.json.name || 'there',\n    _clinic_name: item.json.clinic_name || $env.DEFAULT_CLINIC_NAME || 'our clinic',\n    _doctor_name: item.json.doctor_name || $env.DEFAULT_DOCTOR_NAME || 'your doctor'\n  }\n}));"
      },
      "id": "55555555-5555-5555-5555-000000000004",
      "name": "Filter Inactive Patients",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        680,
        380
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": false,
            "leftValue": "",
            "typeValidation": "loose"
          },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "skip-check-wf5",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json._skip }}",
              "rightValue": true,
              "operator": {
                "type": "boolean",
                "operation": "true"
              }
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "55555555-5555-5555-5555-000000000005",
      "name": "Skip if No Patients",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        900,
        380
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "={{ 'https://graph.facebook.com/v19.0/' + $env.WA_PHONE_NUMBER_ID + '/messages' }}",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "httpHeaderAuth",
        "sendBody": true,
        "contentType": "json",
        "body": "={{ JSON.stringify({ messaging_product: 'whatsapp', to: $json._to_phone, type: 'template', template: { name: 'patient_reactivation', language: { code: $env.WA_LANGUAGE_CODE || 'en' }, components: [{ type: 'body', parameters: [ { type: 'text', text: $json._name }, { type: 'text', text: $json._clinic_name }, { type: 'text', text: $json._doctor_name } ] }] } }) }}",
        "options": {
          "retry": {
            "maxTries": 3,
            "waitBetweenTries": 30000
          }
        }
      },
      "id": "55555555-5555-5555-5555-000000000006",
      "name": "Send Reactivation Message",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        1120,
        280
      ],
      "credentials": {
        "httpHeaderAuth": {
          "id": "REPLACE_WITH_WA_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "WhatsApp Business API"
        }
      },
      "onError": "continueErrorOutput"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "executeQuery",
        "query": "=UPDATE public.patients SET reactivation_sent = TRUE, last_message_sent = NOW(), message_count = message_count + 1, updated_at = NOW() WHERE id = '{{ $('Filter Inactive Patients').item.json.id }}'",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "55555555-5555-5555-5555-000000000007",
      "name": "Update Patient in Supabase",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.postgres",
      "typeVersion": 2.4,
      "position": [
        1340,
        180
      ],
      "credentials": {
        "postgres": {
          "id": "REPLACE_WITH_SUPABASE_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "Supabase DB"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "insert",
        "schema": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "public",
          "mode": "list"
        },
        "table": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "message_logs",
          "mode": "list"
        },
        "columns": {
          "mappingMode": "defineBelow",
          "value": {
            "patient_id": "={{ $('Filter Inactive Patients').item.json.id }}",
            "patient_name": "={{ $('Filter Inactive Patients').item.json.name }}",
            "phone": "={{ $('Filter Inactive Patients').item.json.phone }}",
            "workflow_name": "workflow-5-reactivation",
            "message_type": "reactivation",
            "message_sent": "={{ $('Filter Inactive Patients').item.json._message_body }}",
            "sent_at": "={{ new Date().toISOString() }}",
            "delivery_status": "sent",
            "wa_message_id": "={{ $json.messages?.[0]?.id || '' }}"
          },
          "matchingColumns": [],
          "schema": []
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "55555555-5555-5555-5555-000000000008",
      "name": "Log Message to Supabase",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.postgres",
      "typeVersion": 2.4,
      "position": [
        1340,
        380
      ],
      "credentials": {
        "postgres": {
          "id": "REPLACE_WITH_SUPABASE_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "Supabase DB"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "insert",
        "schema": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "public",
          "mode": "list"
        },
        "table": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "system_logs",
          "mode": "list"
        },
        "columns": {
          "mappingMode": "defineBelow",
          "value": {
            "workflow_name": "workflow-5-reactivation",
            "execution_id": "={{ $execution.id }}",
            "log_level": "ERROR",
            "message": "Failed to send reactivation message",
            "details": "={{ JSON.stringify({ patient_id: $('Filter Inactive Patients').item.json.id, phone: $('Filter Inactive Patients').item.json.phone, error: $json.error?.message || 'HTTP request failed' }) }}"
          },
          "matchingColumns": [],
          "schema": []
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "55555555-5555-5555-5555-000000000009",
      "name": "Log Send Failure to Supabase",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.postgres",
      "typeVersion": 2.4,
      "position": [
        1340,
        520
      ],
      "credentials": {
        "postgres": {
          "id": "REPLACE_WITH_SUPABASE_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "Supabase DB"
        }
      }
    }
  ],
